                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18140112-110-off570 t18140112-110-cd571"></join>, one hat, value 4 s. one pair of boots, value 6 s. a shirt, value 3 s.<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="181401120051"></xptr>and a pair of stockings, value 18 d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
